ty="0.16" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M14 4H2V10.6667C2 11.403 2.59695 12 3.33333 12H12.6667C13.403 12 14 11.403 14 10.6667V4ZM8 10C9.10457 10 10 9.10457 10 8C10 6.89543 9.10457 6 8 6C6.89543 6 6 6.89543 6 8C6 9.10457 6.89543 10 8 10Z" fill="var(--color-sem-icon-primary-default)"></path><path d="M2 3.33331H14V11.3333C14 12.0697 13.403 12.6666 12.6667 12.6666H3.33333C2.59695 12.6666 2 12.0697 2 11.3333V3.33331Z" stroke="var(--color-sem-icon-primary-default)" stroke-width="1.33333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2" stroke="var(--color-sem-icon-primary-default)" stroke-width="1.33333" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></circle><path d="M11.3332 1.33331L12.6665 1.33331" stroke="var(--color-sem-icon-primary-default)" stroke-width="1.33333" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></g><defs><clipPath id="clip0_209_94274"><rect width="16" height="16" fill="white"></rect></clipPath></defs></svg></span><p aria-label="Police responded to reports of an assault. " class="ImageCaption_caption-title__ccyQU" data-testid="caption-title">Police responded to reports of an assault. </p></figcaption></div><p class="Paragraph_paragraph-text__PVKlh " data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="paragraph">Edinburgh <a aria-label="" class="TextLink_text-link__dBSS0 TextLink_enabled__dJF3l" href="https://www.edinburghlive.co.uk/all-about/police-scotland" rel="follow" tabindex="0" target="_self">police</a> have cordoned off a stretch of pavement in the <a aria-label="" class="TextLink_text-link__dBSS0 TextLink_enabled__dJF3l" href="https://www.edinburghlive.co.uk/all-about/edinburgh-city-centre" rel="follow" tabindex="0" target="_self">Pleasance area </a>of the capital following an <a aria-label="" class="TextLink_text-link__dBSS0 TextLink_enabled__dJF3l" href="https://www.edinburghlive.co.uk/all-about/crime" rel="follow" tabindex="0" target="_self">assault</a> on a male.</p><div class="BoxStyles_box-container__Qk3WH BoxStyles_commercial__Wo6Z4 undefined" data-testid="commercial-1" data-position="1"><div data-tmdatatrack="non-content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="commercial" data-tmdatatrack-index="1" data-tmdatatrack-id="placeholder" class="sc-cea6c478-0 cEiapl"><span aria-live="polite" aria-busy="true"><span class="react-loading-skeleton" style="width:100%;height:100%;--base-color:#88888810;--highlight-color:#8888880d">‌</span><br/></span></div></div><p class="Paragraph_paragraph-text__PVKlh " data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="paragraph">Officers say that the incident took place at around 6:20pm on Wednesday January 25 and that they were called to South Bridge to respond to a report of an assault on a 40-year-old man.</p><div class="BoxStyles_box-container__Qk3WH BoxStyles_commercial__Wo6Z4 undefined" data-testid="commercial-2" data-position="2"><div data-tmdatatrack="non-content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="commercial" data-tmdatatrack-index="2" data-tmdatatrack-id="placeholder" class="sc-cea6c478-0 frXQgj"><span aria-live="polite" aria-busy="true"><span class="react-loading-skeleton" style="width:100%;height:100%;--base-color:#88888810;--highlight-color:#8888880d">‌</span><br/></span></div></div><p class="Paragraph_paragraph-text__PVKlh " data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="paragraph">Emergency services remained at the scene of the alleged crime at 9:00pm on Wednesday evening.</p><div class="BoxStyles_box-container__Qk3WH BoxStyles_commercial__Wo6Z4 undefined" data-testid="commercial-3" data-position="3"><div data-tmdatatrack="non-content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="commercial" data-tmdatatrack-index="3" data-tmdatatrack-id="placeholder" class="sc-cea6c478-0 cEiapl"><span aria-live="polite" aria-busy="true"><span class="react-loading-skeleton" style="width:100%;height:100%;--base-color:#88888810;--highlight-color:#8888880d">‌</span><br/></span></div></div><p class="Paragraph_paragraph-text__PVKlh " data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="paragraph"><strong class="Strong_strong__e2x35">READ MORE:</strong> <strong class="Strong_strong__e2x35"><a aria-label="" class="TextLink_text-link__dBSS0 TextLink_enabled__dJF3l" href="https://www.edinburghlive.co.uk/news/edinburgh-news/edinburgh-motorist-unable-work-after-26073394" rel="follow" tabindex="0" target="_self">Edinburgh motorist unable to work after car badly damaged by capital pothole</a></strong></p><p class="Paragraph_paragraph-text__PVKlh " data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="paragraph">One resident captured images of the response with a police officer and van spotted outside the Burrito’n’Shake eatery.</p><p class="Paragraph_paragraph-text__PVKlh " data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="paragraph">Blue and white police tape was in place from outside the restaurant all the way to the end of the neighbouring Edinburgh Heritage.com shop.</p><div class="BoxStyles_box-container__Qk3WH BoxStyles_commercial__Wo6Z4 undefined" data-testid="commercial-4" data-position="5"><div data-tmdatatrack="non-content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="commercial" data-tmdatatrack-index="4" data-tmdatatrack-id="placeholder" class="sc-cea6c478-0 frXQgj"><span aria-live="polite" aria-busy="true"><span class="react-loading-skeleton" style="width:100%;height:100%;--base-color:#88888810;--highlight-color:#8888880d">‌</span><br/></span></div></div><div class="BoxStyles_box-container__Qk3WH BoxStyles_non-commercial__aiWwo undefined" data-testid="non-commercial-1" data-position="6"></div><div data-testid="image-group"><div class="ImageEmbed_image-embed__0T8WX false" data-testid="imageembed-26074117" data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-articleid="26074117" data-tmdatatrack-type="image"><div class="ImageEmbed_image-container__2AIQm"><figure class="Figure_figure__Uce4f" style="--figure-aspect-ratio:1.33"><img alt="Police tape remains at the scene on South Bridge. " loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 458px) 458px, (max-width: 615px) 615px, 1200px" src="https://i2-prod.edinburghlive.co.uk/article26074117.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200e/0_Police-tape-outside-BurritonShake-North-Bridgejpeg.jpg" srcSet="https://i2-prod.edinburghlive.co.uk/article26074117.ece/ALTERNATES/s458b/0_Police-tape-outside-BurritonShake-North-Bridgejpeg.jpg 458w, https://i2-prod.edinburghlive.co.uk/article26074117.ece/ALTERNATES/s615b/0_Police-tape-outside-BurritonShake-North-Bridgejpeg.jpg 615w, https://i2-prod.edinburghlive.co.uk/article26074117.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200e/0_Police-tape-outside-BurritonShake-North-Bridgejpeg.jpg 1200w"/></figure></div><figcaption class="ImageCaption_caption__j7HRu" data-testid="image-caption"><span class="ImageCaption_caption-header__4xmz_" data-testid="caption-header"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><g clip-path="url(#clip0_209_94274)"><path opacity="0.16" fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M14 4H2V10.6667C2 11.403 2.59695 12 3.33333 12H12.6667C13.403 12 14 11.403 14 10.6667V4ZM8 10C9.10457 10 10 9.10457 10 8C10 6.89543 9.10457 6 8 6C6.89543 6 6 6.89543 6 8C6 9.10457 6.89543 10 8 10Z" fill="var(--color-sem-icon-primary-default)"></path><path d="M2 3.33331H14V11.3333C14 12.0697 13.403 12.6666 12.6667 12.6666H3.33333C2.59695 12.6666 2 12.0697 2 11.3333V3.33331Z" stroke="var(--color-sem-icon-primary-default)" stroke-width="1.33333" stroke-linejoin="round"></path><circle cx="8" cy="8" r="2" stroke="var(--color-sem-icon-primary-default)" stroke-width="1.33333" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></circle><path d="M11.3332 1.33331L12.6665 1.33331" stroke="var(--color-sem-icon-primary-default)" stroke-width="1.33333" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"></path></g><defs><clipPath id="clip0_209_94274"><rect width="16" height="16" fill="white"></rect></clipPath></defs></svg></span><p aria-label="Police tape remains at the scene on South Bridge. " class="ImageCaption_caption-title__ccyQU" data-testid="caption-title">Police tape remains at the scene on South Bridge. </p></figcaption></div></div><p class="Paragraph_paragraph-text__PVKlh " data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="paragraph">The street looked relatively calm in the picture shared with Edinburgh Live and police say that the man was taken to hospital for treatment on his injuries.</p><p class="Paragraph_paragraph-text__PVKlh " data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="paragraph">It is understood that pedestrian access to the aforementioned businesses is still blocked off by the police tape whilst officers respond to the incident.</p><div class="BoxStyles_box-container__Qk3WH BoxStyles_commercial__Wo6Z4 undefined" data-testid="commercial-5" data-position="7"><div data-tmdatatrack="non-content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-type="commercial" data-tmdatatrack-index="5" data-tmdatatrack-id="placeholder" class="sc-cea6c478-0 eqzKJa"><span aria-live="polite" aria-busy="true"><span class="react-loading-skeleton" style="width:100%;height:100%;--base-color:#88888810;--highlight-color:#8888880d">‌</span><br/></span></div></div><div data-testid="image-group"><div class="ImageEmbed_image-embed__0T8WX false" data-testid="imageembed-26074126" data-tmdatatrack="content-unit" data-tmdatatrack-articleid="26074126" data-tmdatatrack-type="image"><div class="ImageEmbed_image-container__2AIQm"><figure class="Figure_figure__Uce4f" style="--figure-aspect-ratio:1.33"><img alt="Police tape is blocking off the stretch of pavement. " loading="lazy" sizes="(max-width: 458px) 458px, (max-width: 615px) 615px, 1200px" src="https://i2-prod.edinburghlive.co.uk/article26074126.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200e/0_The-tape-also-stretched-to-Heritage-of-Edinburgh-dot-comjpeg.jpg" srcSet="https://i2-prod.edinburghlive.co.uk/article26074126.ece/ALTERNATES/s458b/0_The-tape-also-stretched-to-Heritage-of-Edinburgh-dot-comjpeg.jpg 458w, https://i2-prod.edinburghlive.co.uk/article26074126.ece/ALTERNATES/s615b/0_The-tape-also-stretched-to-Heritage-